<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include("partials/head", {
    pageTitle: "Software Engineering"
  }) %>

  <body>
    <%- include("partials/nav") %>

    <main>
      <section class="page-title">
        <p class="eyebrow">Building reliable systems</p>
        <h1>Software Engineering</h1>

        <p>
          Software engineers combine technical skills, planning,
          testing, and teamwork to solve problems.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="two-column">
        <article>
          <h2>What Software Engineers Do</h2>

          <p>
            Software engineers use computer science concepts to
            solve problems. They design systems, write code, test
            programs, fix bugs, and improve software over time.
          </p>

          <p>
            They also work with teams, use version control, and
            follow project requirements. This helps make software
            more reliable and easier to maintain.
          </p>
        </article>

        <figure>
          <img
            src="/img/software.jpg"
            alt="Software engineering workspace"
          >
        </figure>
      </section>

      <section class="info-box">
        <h2>Common Software Engineering Skills</h2>

        <ul class="skills-list">
          <li>Problem solving</li>
          <li>Programming</li>
          <li>Testing and debugging</li>
          <li>Version control with Git</li>
          <li>Team communication</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
  </body>
</html>